                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310217-131-victim1349 t18310217-131-viclabel779"></join>, of Ludgate-hill. On the 12th of February I bought three flats of butter of Hill, a salesman, in <placeName id="t18310217-131-crimeloc780">Newgate-market</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310217-131-crimeloc780" type="placeName" value="Newgate-market"></interp>
